@node "EDITO" "EDITORIAL ..."
@toc "MAIN"

 @{"MAIN MENU" LINK "MAIN"} 
 
    
     WELL IT'S HERE ! THE FIRST ISSUE OF A.G.P [AMIGA GAME PROJECT], WE
     DECIDED TO RELEASE THIS LITTLE INFO FILE ABOUT ALL SOON COMING
     GAMES, THERE ARE A LOT OF PAPER MAGS OVER THE WORLD ABOUT THE AMIGA
     AND ALL THE LATEST GAMES SOON TO BE RELEASED ON OUR LOVELY MACHINE.
     WE'VE JUST TRIED TO DO, A USEFULL LITTLE SUMMARY OF ALL THE LATEST 
     GAMES IN PROGRESS THAT WILL BE SOON RELEASED. SO IF YOU ARE A
     MAIL TRADER, MODEM TRADER, OR IF YOU JUST LIKE PLAYING GAMES, YOU
     ARE MOST PROBABLY INTERESTED TO KNOW WHICH GAMES WILL SOON BE OUT, 
     WHEN IT WILL BE RELEASED, OR WHAT ARE THE PROJECTS OF SOME COMPANIES
     WITH THIS FILE YOU HAVE EVERYTHING IN ONE FILE !!

     ALL GAMES ARE CLASSIFIED BY COMPANIES, WITH ALL INFOS ABOUT: DATE -
     SUPPORTED MACHINES [ECS - AGA - CD32] AND THE STYLE OF GAME [SPORT -
     SHOOT'EM UP - ADVENTURE - STRATEGY - BEAT'EM UP - SIMULATION -
     ROLE PLAYING GAME - ARCADE - WARGAME - PLATFORM] IN FACT ALL THE 
     REAL INFOS YOU NEED TO KNOW ABOUT GAMES. 

     I JUST HOPE YOU WILL APPRECIATE ALL THE WORK THAT HAS BEEN DONE TO
     COLLECT ALL INFOS NEEDED TO RELEASE A.G.P !!! 
     
     THE NEXT ISSUE WILL BE RELEASED IN NOVEMBER [15 NOVEMBER]

	GANDALF & WONDER / OUTLAWS

@endnode
